\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No, it\rquote s after that.
