\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No. She was one that - that told Lou that she - she\rquote d got some pictures she painted there, this Mrs - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10833110\charrsid13385743 Irishwoman}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  - Middleton and she told him she painted them in paraffin you know and he wouldn\rquote t believe her you know, you\rquote 
re kidding me he said.
