\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, at one time a girl used to come in. What was her name, she used to pinch the toffee. I can\rquote t - I don\rquote 
