\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10833110\charrsid13385743 Phyllis}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  and Mildred. Oh yes, and there was another room tucked in between there and they had it that\rquote 
