\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did he show affection?
