 days do you. There was sort of doctors, I suppose you - sort of thought were important. Perhaps clergy. And - I remember there was a wealthy man, Mr End in Croydon Road there. He was a - a - you know he was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
