\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well only the shops of course were employers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What sort of people would you say went to the church and to the chapel, did you notice any difference between the two types?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 I didn\rquote t at that stage of my life. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Where you lived did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14572883\charrsid13385743 say there}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  were different groups within in the group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well in Stoddart Road for instance they were more or less on - all on a similar standard. This is a rather - infinite question isn
\rquote t it, it\rquote s - I mean it can vary even there couldn\rquote t it. Some people appear well off, I mean, you know, or make it - make it look as though they\rquote re well off on nothing can\rquote t they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 So really you would say there were different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well we - well there\rquote s always the poorer people. Arpley Road we always considered the - the you know - I mean, you can\rquote 
t - you\rquote ve got to face it, there was - there was a difference, you used to get all your ragged sort of gutter - gutter }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14682021\charrsid13385743 kids}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  in some areas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you think that one group felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well I can\rquote t answer for groups really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Were some families thought of as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 I would say so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Can\rquote t recall any. From my own experience.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Mother - I suppose, did - she was very class conscious I think. I don\rquote t - I - I never heard my father expound his views. He was 
always putting the world right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class, she did didn\rquote t she?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you know why? Was she thinking of her parents, her work before she married, the house where she lived or your father\rquote s job?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Oh definitely - her - where she lived and that you know, that was considered - St - was it St James\rquote s - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Before she was married this is?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes. Grange Road or Upper Grange Road - considered high class in those - in her days - in those days in the late 1900\rquote s.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you think when she married your father she thought she was sort of marrying beneath her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Was it possible at that time to move from one class or group to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well is it now come to that. I wouldn\rquote t know would I, I mean, I - you see, don\rquote t forget I was only young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 You didn\rquote t remember anyone who did sort of go up in the world or somebody who went down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No, because - I mean, if people come from a - what we call a lower class, they bring; the environment with them don\rquote 
t they, they don\rquote t change over night do they. Some people make a sort of try - effort, don\rquote t they, to change their status.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 But you can\rquote t remember anybody who did that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No, I can\rquote t remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, the ordinary man on the beat used to come there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What did you think of him? When you were naughty did your mother ever say, I\rquote ll call a policeman?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 I don\rquote t think she ever used those words to us. I\rquote ve heard people say it but - I don\rquote t think we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14682021\charrsid13385743 ever}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  regarded him as - terrifying or anything like that. You know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 You didn\rquote t take much notice of him then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No. Indifferent almost.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How do you think he treated the people generally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Quite - quite well actually. No - no - they didn\rquote 
t sort of interfere with anybody, you know, they were well conducted people and all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Your home was rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you see anything of the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No. It was done through an agent I think. Forget who we used to pay - Noyes and Howes I think, something like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you remember feeling that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What did you think about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 I thought it needn\rquote t have happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What difference did it make to the family when your father was ill or out or work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well it meant times of stress financially and - as I say - well a shortage of necessities almost.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Can you remember how often he was out of work or ill? Was it quite a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No. He was in a job twenty-five years that he left in 19 - 1916 or something like that - \rquote 1
7 probably. They went into liquidation. That started the rot you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Was that when he started drinking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No, no, he\rquote 
d met his drinking pals going up to town every day on the train. There was a Frenchman named Marchade. A bank clerk I think he was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you ever have to get help from the guardians or the parish or any sort of charity?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 He did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Your father went to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Father went to them, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you remember how they treated him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well I think he was pretty plausible and they - he got by all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did you feel about him going there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Not very happy. You\rquote re learning a lot aren\rquote t you Jan?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 I didn\rquote t even now about him getting into trouble?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 That he went into jail. Oh yes, he got four months. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What did he do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Oh he - he cooked the wages things you know. No he didn\rquote t. Yes he did. He was working for Ashbury\rquote s the Bond Street }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14572883\charrsid13385743 jewellers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 , you know - you know them don\rquote t you. Yes. It was them that pinched him. Got him pinched. Oh yes. And I - that 
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14682021\charrsid13385743 wasn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  so - I can remember - I don\rquote t know when - I don\rquote t want to record this but I don\rquote 
t know when he left George Partridge where he\rquote d been twenty-five years in Bishopsgate, one firm, but - he must have been somewhere else before that becaus
e he got - he got - he was in Woolwich - Woolwich Arsenal there and - he started - he started it there. Falsifying the wages sheets. He got it away with it there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Was he a wages clerk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No, he wasn\rquote t really, he was a - I think he was a - accounts
 clerk like me. I think that Ashbury business was his second attempt. They prosecuted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 
When there was someone in the district whom the people disapproved of very strongly was there any special way in which they showed it, do you remember anyone being made to leave by rough music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Do you remember an effigy being made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Were you given your lessons by one of your parents a tutor or governess?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 You went straight to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 School, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Six. Six years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 When you first started what time of the morning did you go and when did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Nine to - nine o\rquote clock \lquote til four. Used to come home for dinner. Then back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 12 \lquote til one thirty dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes. It was - it was at St Johns, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 You always went to school full time, you didn\rquote t start going at first only in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 A church school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Was it a boys and girls mixed school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Boys school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Walked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14572883\charrsid13385743 How long did it take you?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Ten minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Nobody.
