\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well you\rquote d probably get told off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did they punish the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well either with the cane or lines I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What sort of things would you be punished for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Oh - I think it probably depended on the teacher\rquote s liver.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork? Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 I don\rquote t think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did they visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Although I think mother used to keep a sort of watching brief, you know, how we were getting on and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did they visit the school or meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Mainly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Why would that be, were they a bit brighter than the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No, I think they were pretty fair that way, I don\rquote t think they took advantage of dull kids you know. But - there\rquote 
s some sort of - children I suppose - a bit - what }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14572883\charrsid13385743 shall}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  we say, I don\rquote t wan
t to say obnoxious but - unappealing to some people. To quite a lot of people perhaps. Just by their conduct you know and that soft or thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14572883\charrsid13385743 It wasn't anything to do with the sort of background they came from?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well it could be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 I don\rquote t remember any.
