\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 
Yes. Probably. Do you want any more answer than that. Oh well, I feel I could have got a better position if I had had, you know, better education.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Further education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
