\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 A shilling for the Saturday. I know I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you feel that was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, I didn\rquote t really do it for the money so much in those days as for something to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you give any of that money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, I used to give her the bob and she used - probably give me tuppence back or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 And that still went in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 And how did you get on with the other people you worked with there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well they were very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Oh, quite ordinary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did you feel about him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Quite all right, we were good friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you like this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Which one\rquote s that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 The baker\rquote s round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, I was quite happy at it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 They were the only two jobs you had while you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes. No, I didn\rquote t really I went - I went up to - I left the bakers round didn\rquote 
t I and I went to work in a house, up at Avenue Road, South Norwood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What were you doing up there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well just a sort of Saturday morning odd job boy you know. Cleaning up things, tidying up. Sweeping up the leaves in the gard
en. It was the old cook there, I used to deliver bread there see and she asked me if I\rquote d like to change me job. I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14572883\charrsid13385743 don\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  know whether it was more money, it might have been. I used to walk home the-e, right up South Norwood Hill, down here, I can remember coming home through Hamlet Road and - that - that was a bit boring that job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 That was Saturday again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Saturday job only, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How long did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Not very long there. Probably four to six months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What sort of hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Oh about nine \lquote til two or something like that I would think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 You don\rquote t remember what you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14572883\charrsid13385743 paid}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No, I don\rquote t - I - I think - I\rquote m not sure whether it was the same money as for the baker or - it probably was. I don\rquote 
t think there was any inducement there to - it was just a change of occupation. Talk - the old cook talked me into it you know. That was the Mayes, the hop people that had a place in the Borough there, W.H. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9647493 &
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  H. Le Maye. I never saw the - guv\rquote nor himself, or very seldom. I think he had been about once or twice although I never -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 You didn\rquote t have much to do with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No. It was all done through the cook you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you get on all right with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did you get on with the other people you worked with, there was the cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Were there any more people there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No, as I say, I never - I never seemed to see anybody much there at all. I think the guv\rquote nor, you know, Mr Lemaye w
ent to work Saturday mornings and he probably - he - he was only just about home by the time I left. Just got a recollection of seeing a portly man once or twice in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What was your first full time job when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What do you want, clerical do you mean or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Your first job when you went to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 You went into an office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes. I went straight into accounts really, I wasn\rquote t - I wasn\rquote t an office boy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did you get this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 From the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Oh I was learning bought ledger accounts really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 This was for Wright Layman and Umney?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What hours did you work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Eight \lquote til six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you work Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Or Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, Saturday morning. Eight \lquote til one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you have a half day at all during the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No. Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Can you remember what your wage was when you first started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, ten bob a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you feel that was a fair wage not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 It was practically about normal for the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, all of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What was it spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well I had to have some back for fares out of that, two bob a week for fares for a start. Well general household expenses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did you get on with the other people you worked with there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Quite all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did your employer treat you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well quite normally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Almost indifferent because it didn\rquote t - it didn't affect me much the governors there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 How did you feel about the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, it was all right - I could do it so it didn\rquote t bother me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did the job alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What jobs have you done since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 The same one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Would you have preferred another type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes, I think I might have liked to have done manual work perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 What type of manual work - a trade or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Yes. I probably wouldn\rquote t have minded being a carpenter or something like that. I didn\rquote 
t have any option, I was just pushed into it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you serve an apprenticeship or training period for your job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you belong to any trade union or professional organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 It }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14682021\charrsid13385743 depends}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  what they mean by interest, I mean - what do they mean - attitude to the job? Well it\rquote s the same as it is now, the governors only looking for profit }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14572883\charrsid13385743 margin}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743  and the worker\rquote s always looking for money and wages, higher wages. There\rquote s no sort of alteration in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among workers themselves?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Not particularly in those days. Things were fairly settled you know, everybody sort of had their work to do and they did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers, did you feel that or not?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9112736 GR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Well I still think that applies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7691827 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11101550\charrsid13385743 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
